    "What is unclear from the Hameroff and Penrose proposal is how the collapse of the quantum wavefunction should create some conscious percept (qualia) such as the taste of chocolate, which suggests that their Orch OR theory (Hameroff and Penrose, 2014, 2017; Hameroff, 2021) is at least incomplete."
